<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>A Small Adventure 🤍</title>
<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
  background:#ffeef3;
  text-align:center;
}
.box{
  background:white;
  padding:30px;
  border-radius:20px;
  width:85%;
  max-width:450px;
  box-shadow:0 5px 20px #0002;
}
button{
  padding:12px 20px;
  margin:10px;
  border:none;
  border-radius:25px;
  background:#ff7fa3;
  color:white;
  font-size:16px;
  cursor:pointer;
}
#moving{
  position:relative;
}
.hidden{display:none;}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="box">

<div id="p1">
<h1>Welcome to the game 🤍</h1>
<p>Player name: <b>Mercy Yongtahu</b></p>
<p>Ready for a small adventure?</p>
<button onclick="next(2)">Hell yeahhh! 🤍</button>
</div>


<div id="p2" class="hidden">
<h1>Memories 🤍</h1>

<p>Do you still remember our first days together?</p>
<button onclick="next(3)">Yes🤍</button>
<button onclick="next(3)">Obviously😂</button>

<p>Do you know how special you are to me?</p>
<button onclick="next(3)">Yes🤞</button>
<button id="moving" onmouseover="move(this)">Tell me again 🥹</button>
</div>


<div id="p3" class="hidden">
<h1>Questions 😌</h1>

<p>Who loves more? ❤️</p>
<button id="love" onmouseover="moveFew(this)">Me</button>
<button onclick="alert('Correct answer 🤍')">You</button>

<p>Who is more annoying? 😂</p>
<button id="annoy" onmouseover="moveFew(this)">You 🙄</button>
<button onclick="alert('See? You know it 😌🤍')">Me 🤭</button>

<p>Would you choose me again?</p>
<button onclick="next(4)">Yes🤍</button>
<button id="no" onmouseover="move(this)">No</button>

</div>


<div id="p4" class="hidden">
<h1>The Heart Message 🤍</h1>
<p>
I know we’ve had ups and downs. We’ve made mistakes, we’ve grown, and we’ve changed…
but one thing I never want to lose is the bond we have.
<br><br>
Thankyou for still being here, for understanding me, and for being someone who makes my days better🤍
</p>

<button onclick="next(5)">Continue 🤍</button>
</div>


<div id="p5" class="hidden">
<h1>Big Question 🤍</h1>

<p>Will you continue making more memories with me?</p>

<button onclick="finish()">Yes🤍</button>
<button id="finalNo" onmouseover="move(this)">No</button>

</div>


<div id="done" class="hidden">
<h1>🤍</h1>
<p>
Thankyou for choosing me again.
<br><br>
I’ll keep trying to become someone who deserves your love🤍
</p>
</div>


</div>


<script>

function next(page){
 document.querySelectorAll(".box > div").forEach(x=>x.classList.add("hidden"));
 document.getElementById("p"+page).classList.remove("hidden");
}

function finish(){
 document.querySelectorAll(".box > div").forEach(x=>x.classList.add("hidden"));
 document.getElementById("done").classList.remove("hidden");
}

function move(btn){
 btn.style.transform=
 `translate(${Math.random()*250-125}px,${Math.random()*150-75}px)`;
}

function moveFew(btn){
 btn.style.transform=
 `translate(${Math.random()*120-60}px,${Math.random()*80-40}px)`;
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
